{"tid":1474280,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【政治教育電視】我地整咗條片講「甚麼是警察國家？」","createTime":"2019-08-15T06:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T13:48:50.000Z","uid":264620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e240ccd774bf6786693e5d60e699c403ed30dcf0","tid":1474280,"uid":264620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:18:52.000Z","msg":"我地整咗條片，講咩係「警察國家」<br />\n<br />\n本來諗住自己寫，但發現鄭立喺2016年時已在立場出文，講嘅嘢都好中，所以我地就用返佢篇文嚟做片，希望畀啲唔想睇字嘅人都可以聽下，youtube 無聊時都可以睇下。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xix2DMHdLXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fxix2DMHdLXc&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=89e9ed07\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xix2DMHdLXc</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook 版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ProjectCanto/videos/428916807710730/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FProjectCanto%2Fvideos%2F428916807710730%2F&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=f84b7d1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ProjectCanto/videos/428916807710730/</a><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊都會繼續做「政治教育電視」，因為有感文宣量多，有啲內容已發展到比較深入，可能會有人唔清楚，所以想喺大家於前線做文宣時，我地試下做返啲BB班嘢。<br />\n<br />\n不過因為人手都係得幾隻，暫時我地都係搵下文章去砌片，都會有自己寫嘅但唔多，<br />\n所以都希望大家畀下意見，關於改善又好，題目又好，歡迎提出，感謝，大家加油。<br />\n<br />\nbtw，如果有writer底嘅人又可以寫下文幫下手，可以搵我地：<a href=\"https://t.me/projectcanto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fprojectcanto&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=15ffa102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/projectcanto</a><br />\n<br />\n最後要多謝返鄭立先生授權～"},{"pid":"1d4d9a02ac4210064932b3215161cc4b51dc0c44","tid":1474280,"uid":295889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正經post冇人推！？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Set deadline再升級係大多手足嘅共識 大家一齊去